          instruction: "While grill heats, place garlic on cutting board and sprinkle with salt. Mash to paste with side of knife. Transfer garlic paste to disposable pan. Add cilantro, pepper, remaining 1/4 cup vinegar, and remaining 1/4 cup oil and mix to form paste."
